WEBVTT

00:00:11.800 --> 00:00:12.679
What are you looking at me for?

00:00:13.199 --> 00:00:14.679
The scrapyard isn't open anyway.

00:00:22.359 --> 00:00:24.679
If I'm not mistaken,

00:00:26.000 --> 00:00:27.039
you've got a new boss, right?

00:00:28.280 --> 00:00:29.359
Why do you care?

00:00:33.399 --> 00:00:34.359
I'll give you this much.

00:00:36.880 --> 00:00:37.439
Six.

00:00:37.439 --> 00:00:38.280
Two thousand.

00:00:39.799 --> 00:00:40.640
Two thousand?

00:00:41.000 --> 00:00:41.840
For this?

00:00:43.039 --> 00:00:44.039
Are your eyes playing tricks on you?

00:00:44.439 --> 00:00:45.159
You selling or not?

00:00:51.079 --> 00:00:51.799
Young man,

00:00:52.560 --> 00:00:53.439
how about six thousand?

00:00:53.520 --> 00:00:54.640
Quite valuable, huh.

00:00:54.799 --> 00:00:56.159
Six thousand five hundred works too.

00:01:02.119 --> 00:01:02.920
Now,

00:01:03.399 --> 00:01:04.719
we can get down to business.

00:01:11.920 --> 00:01:12.640
Datou,

00:01:17.799 --> 00:01:19.439
if Brother Mao had been

00:01:20.239 --> 00:01:21.480
at the explosion site today,

00:01:23.040 --> 00:01:23.879
what would've happened?

00:01:28.200 --> 00:01:29.079
Same as now.

00:01:49.519 --> 00:01:51.040
Min's already taken the bait.

00:01:51.519 --> 00:01:53.959
The cops must be hunting him everywhere.

00:01:55.560 --> 00:01:56.879
Where do we meet tomorrow?

00:01:57.640 --> 00:01:58.879
I'll hand the stuff over to you.

00:01:59.599 --> 00:02:00.680
We're not meeting.

00:02:02.000 --> 00:02:03.359
Tomorrow at three p.m.,

00:02:03.760 --> 00:02:05.920
leave it by the green trash can

00:02:06.000 --> 00:02:07.280
on Dongsikou South Road.

00:02:20.639 --> 00:02:21.319
Honey,

00:02:21.960 --> 00:02:23.120
how's everything on your end?

00:02:25.680 --> 00:02:27.960
The results came back. It's

00:02:28.759 --> 00:02:29.960
Fanconi anemia.

00:02:30.159 --> 00:02:32.680
The doctor says it's a rare blood disease.

00:02:35.400 --> 00:02:36.800
She has to be hospitalized right away?

00:02:37.520 --> 00:02:38.439
We

00:02:40.599 --> 00:02:42.280
have to stay for more tests.

00:02:45.400 --> 00:02:47.240
I suppose that's a good thing.

00:02:47.439 --> 00:02:48.520
It's still in the early stage,

00:02:48.680 --> 00:02:50.039
and there are plenty of treatment options.

00:02:50.879 --> 00:02:51.919
It's just that

00:02:53.759 --> 00:02:55.599
the costs, conservatively estimated,

00:02:55.680 --> 00:02:56.759
will be around 600,000.

00:02:57.400 --> 00:02:58.919
Don't you worry

00:02:59.840 --> 00:03:01.000
about the money.

00:03:01.719 --> 00:03:03.159
Getting her better is what matters.

00:03:03.360 --> 00:03:04.520
I'll handle the money.

00:03:04.520 --> 00:03:06.000
I... I'll figure something out.

00:03:06.800 --> 00:03:07.599
Don't worry.

00:03:12.159 --> 00:03:12.919
Where's Paopao?

00:03:13.000 --> 00:03:14.159
Is Paopao with you?

00:03:14.280 --> 00:03:15.360
Yes, hold on a second.

00:03:16.879 --> 00:03:17.639
Paopao,

00:03:17.960 --> 00:03:19.080
it's Daddy on the phone.

00:03:20.719 --> 00:03:21.680
Daddy!

00:03:34.680 --> 00:03:35.439
Chief Wang,

00:03:35.800 --> 00:03:37.080
I suspect this bombing case

00:03:37.360 --> 00:03:38.719
is connected to Feng Mao Company.

00:03:39.159 --> 00:03:40.080
The suspect, Min Shengquan,

00:03:40.159 --> 00:03:42.360
his motive for the bombing is unclear.

00:03:43.039 --> 00:03:44.360
But the victim, Zhang Yuanshan,

00:03:44.520 --> 00:03:46.159
used to run Yuanshan Auto Repair,

00:03:46.439 --> 00:03:47.599
which was later bought out by Luo Xiao.

00:03:47.759 --> 00:03:48.759
Because of that, Zhang Yuanshan

00:03:48.840 --> 00:03:50.240
caused trouble for Luo Xiao many times.

00:03:50.759 --> 00:03:51.520
Meanwhile,

00:03:51.639 --> 00:03:54.319
ever since Luo Xiao left Daoze Law Firm,

00:03:54.479 --> 00:03:56.479
that Shi Qijun has frequently shown up

00:03:56.479 --> 00:03:57.479
at that auto repair shop.

00:03:57.719 --> 00:03:58.639
More importantly,

00:03:58.840 --> 00:04:01.080
the Shengquan Company controlled by Min

00:04:01.159 --> 00:04:03.039
has close ties with Feng Mao Company.

00:04:03.319 --> 00:04:05.560
Their financial dealings are complex and abnormal.

00:04:06.159 --> 00:04:07.919
When you connect all these clues,

00:04:08.400 --> 00:04:09.879
things are probably not that simple.

00:04:10.479 --> 00:04:11.879
I believe this bombing case

00:04:12.479 --> 00:04:14.319
involves multiple parties behind the scenes.

00:04:14.639 --> 00:04:16.480
We might've been used as pawns.

00:04:17.120 --> 00:04:17.839
So,

00:04:18.040 --> 00:04:18.839
the scope of the investigation

00:04:18.959 --> 00:04:20.079
should be expanded further.

00:04:24.759 --> 00:04:26.000
Since things are suspicious,

00:04:26.920 --> 00:04:28.879
we'll get to the bottom of it.

00:04:29.879 --> 00:04:30.759
No matter

00:04:31.920 --> 00:04:33.040
who's behind it,

00:04:33.759 --> 00:04:35.639
no matter how far it reaches,

00:04:35.759 --> 00:04:37.240
we must investigate thoroughly by the law.

00:04:38.279 --> 00:04:39.240
No leniency.

00:04:40.199 --> 00:04:41.279
I'll get the job done.

00:05:01.759 --> 00:05:02.439
Hey, Chen.

00:05:03.079 --> 00:05:03.680
Come here.

00:05:03.920 --> 00:05:04.879
Wash the car for me,

00:05:05.839 --> 00:05:06.759
and then, uh,

00:05:07.439 --> 00:05:08.319
give it a tune-up too.

00:05:08.519 --> 00:05:09.600
My friends will have

00:05:09.720 --> 00:05:11.800
about four cars coming over soon.

00:05:41.399 --> 00:05:42.120
Who is it?

00:05:42.720 --> 00:05:43.439
Hmph.

00:06:02.439 --> 00:06:04.600
What took you so long?

00:06:04.800 --> 00:06:05.399
What are you doing here?

00:06:05.399 --> 00:06:06.319
Should I take off my shoes?

00:06:06.879 --> 00:06:07.439
Come on in.

00:06:07.480 --> 00:06:08.319
Don't you have work?

00:06:09.120 --> 00:06:10.680
Didn't my sister tell you?

00:06:10.959 --> 00:06:14.120
She was worried a six-hour round trip would be too much for you.

00:06:14.199 --> 00:06:15.639
We'll take turns. I took the day off.

00:06:16.079 --> 00:06:18.199
Six hours, we'll be there before you know it.

00:06:19.800 --> 00:06:21.120
Aren't you really busy lately?

00:06:21.120 --> 00:06:23.199
I heard that bombing case is a big deal.

00:06:24.959 --> 00:06:26.040
Yeah, that bombing case.

00:06:26.439 --> 00:06:27.560
It involves a lot of things.

00:06:27.639 --> 00:06:28.839
Enough to keep me busy for a while.

00:06:31.720 --> 00:06:32.800
I heard on the news

00:06:32.959 --> 00:06:34.160
nobody was killed, right?

00:06:34.720 --> 00:06:35.879
And you guys can't catch the suspect?

00:06:41.279 --> 00:06:42.560
What's that smell in here?

00:06:47.839 --> 00:06:48.879
The moment I walked in,

00:06:50.560 --> 00:06:52.000
I smelled something weird.

00:07:00.639 --> 00:07:01.839
Did you crap in here?

00:07:05.160 --> 00:07:06.160
No, I mean, look at this...

00:07:06.240 --> 00:07:07.399
Open the windows!

00:07:07.480 --> 00:07:09.439
This place looks like a storage room.

00:07:12.360 --> 00:07:13.399
Your sister's not home.

00:07:13.480 --> 00:07:14.879
On my own,

00:07:15.199 --> 00:07:16.000
I get a bit sloppy.

00:07:16.480 --> 00:07:17.600
The trash and all,

00:07:17.959 --> 00:07:18.759
I haven't taken it out.

00:07:19.160 --> 00:07:20.839
You really do need my sister, don't you?

00:07:22.000 --> 00:07:22.600
Yeah.

00:07:22.680 --> 00:07:24.360
Paopao's grandma told me to bring these over.

00:07:24.480 --> 00:07:26.639
They were left at her place, so I'll just put them...

00:07:28.480 --> 00:07:29.639
These are for Paopao, right?

00:07:30.360 --> 00:07:31.279
I'll pack them in here.

00:07:32.000 --> 00:07:32.879
That stuff,

00:07:33.079 --> 00:07:34.240
don't forget to bring it.

00:07:34.800 --> 00:07:35.639
Not bad.

00:07:39.800 --> 00:07:40.759
This bag of yours...

00:07:41.160 --> 00:07:42.279
If I remember right,

00:07:42.439 --> 00:07:44.079
it's older than Paopao, isn't it?

00:07:45.759 --> 00:07:48.160
Still won't replace it? Look, it's all worn out.

00:07:50.879 --> 00:07:51.800
I'm sentimental.

00:07:52.560 --> 00:07:53.399
It's an old bag.

00:07:53.920 --> 00:07:55.879
Over a decade. I can't bear to toss it.

00:07:56.759 --> 00:07:57.839
It still works fine.

00:07:58.360 --> 00:07:59.079
Let's get going.

00:07:59.160 --> 00:08:00.480
It's a long drive.

00:08:00.680 --> 00:08:01.480
Alright, let's go.

00:08:01.680 --> 00:08:02.519
Let's take my car.

00:08:03.079 --> 00:08:03.959
Sure, let's go.

00:08:04.240 --> 00:08:04.839
You don't need to carry it.

00:08:04.839 --> 00:08:06.560
Anyway, go take out that trash now.

00:08:06.639 --> 00:08:07.560
Hurry up and toss it.

00:08:07.839 --> 00:08:08.519
Okay, okay, okay.

00:08:08.920 --> 00:08:10.519
It reeks. Seriously.

00:08:28.199 --> 00:08:29.199
Wait for me a second.

00:08:29.279 --> 00:08:30.360
I need to hit the restroom.

00:09:40.360 --> 00:09:41.240
Why'd you come over?

00:09:43.279 --> 00:09:44.960
I noticed you didn't grab any toilet paper.

00:09:45.120 --> 00:09:46.480
I almost couldn't catch up to you.

00:09:47.200 --> 00:09:48.120
What are you doing?

00:09:50.360 --> 00:09:51.399
Looking... looking for the restroom.

00:09:51.480 --> 00:09:52.559
I couldn't find it for a while.

00:09:56.600 --> 00:09:57.720
It says "Public Restroom" right here.

00:10:03.879 --> 00:10:05.759
You're right. Right under my nose.

00:10:54.360 --> 00:10:55.159
What are you up to?

00:10:56.600 --> 00:10:57.440
Waiting for you.

00:10:59.200 --> 00:11:01.360
Weren't you gonna buy chestnut pastries? Come on.

00:11:01.639 --> 00:11:02.840
Yeah, I was waiting to go with you.

00:11:03.039 --> 00:11:03.559
Let's go.

00:11:36.399 --> 00:11:38.200
Any leads from the little plaza?

00:11:38.679 --> 00:11:40.559
Xiao Ru and I checked the street cameras.

00:11:40.840 --> 00:11:42.000
But the coverage is limited.

00:11:42.159 --> 00:11:43.480
Just a small area by the entrance.

00:11:43.799 --> 00:11:45.440
The only footage of Luo Xiao

00:11:46.159 --> 00:11:47.919
is outside the chestnut pastry shop.

00:11:48.639 --> 00:11:49.799
But nothing looked out of the ordinary.

00:11:50.399 --> 00:11:51.639
And you were there too, boss.

00:11:52.399 --> 00:11:53.240
No way.

00:11:53.720 --> 00:11:54.919
Did you check the trash cans?

00:11:55.240 --> 00:11:57.159
I went through them thoroughly.

00:11:57.360 --> 00:11:58.600
I think

00:11:58.720 --> 00:12:00.519
if there was any item exchanged,

00:12:01.480 --> 00:12:02.720
it's probably already been taken.

00:12:04.519 --> 00:12:05.440
Besides,

00:12:05.559 --> 00:12:06.679
the surrounding area is a produce market.

00:12:07.000 --> 00:12:07.919
There's a lot of foot traffic.

00:12:08.440 --> 00:12:09.320
It's hard to track anyone down.

00:12:10.039 --> 00:12:10.879
A produce market?

00:12:11.639 --> 00:12:12.559
Which one?

00:12:13.360 --> 00:12:14.279
Dongsheng Market.

00:12:15.720 --> 00:12:17.000
The one next to Dasheng Temple.

00:12:17.360 --> 00:12:18.000
Right.

00:12:19.600 --> 00:12:20.240
Okay.

00:12:20.320 --> 00:12:21.840
Got it. Hanging up.

00:12:26.480 --> 00:12:27.519
Work call, huh?

00:12:28.159 --> 00:12:29.440
No, Yaping.

00:12:30.000 --> 00:12:31.240
Told me to bring you guys back.

00:12:31.240 --> 00:12:32.879
Said I have to drag all three of you

00:12:32.960 --> 00:12:33.799
home for dinner.

00:12:36.480 --> 00:12:38.039
Good thing it wasn't a work call.

00:12:38.440 --> 00:12:39.879
Otherwise I'd think you suspected me

00:12:39.879 --> 00:12:40.840
and you were here to arrest me.

00:12:41.759 --> 00:12:42.759
Have you broken the law?

00:12:43.600 --> 00:12:44.639
I don't have any evidence.

00:12:45.120 --> 00:12:46.000
You guys

00:12:46.200 --> 00:12:47.440
have to rely on evidence.

00:12:47.960 --> 00:12:48.960
It's a society of laws now.

00:12:48.960 --> 00:12:50.080
You can't just arrest people randomly.

00:12:50.279 --> 00:12:51.200
Right, right.

00:12:51.360 --> 00:12:52.159
We go by evidence.

00:12:54.840 --> 00:12:55.879
Do you know Ruan Chen?

00:12:59.799 --> 00:13:00.480
Who?